Sri Lanka to Borrow $500 Million From Banks to Resurface Roads

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e
-- 
2011-03-03T04:32:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-03/sri-lanka-to-borrow-500-million-from-banks-to-resurface-roads.html
  Sri Lanka  plans to borrow $500
million from local banks on a treasury guarantee to fund a
project for domestic contractors to rehabilitate about 600
kilometers of roads with concrete surfacing, the government said
on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
